{"title":"New Commencal Meta SX reshapes AM enduro bike into a more capable Mullet","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/05/new-commencal-meta-sx-reshapes-am-enduro-bike-into-a-more-capable-mullet/","date":1633459448000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"444\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset-800x444.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset-800x444.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset-297x165.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset-768x427.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset-1536x853.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143328/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_sunset.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-273629\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Commencal’s new 2022 Meta SX reimagines their long-running Meta AM enduro bike platform, refining the bike’s suspension and geometry once again, now optimized for peak performance with a mullet 27.5/29″ wheel combo. The new Meta SX doesn’t replace the recent Meta AM 29, but instead reshapes that bike with a ground-up redesigned mixed wheelsize setup that Commencal says is “<em>more agile and easier in the steeps, more efficient under braking, and more dynamic when pushing hard.</em>”</p><h2>2022 Commencal Meta SX mullet enduro bike</h2><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ih1X0IMYi-I?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>Keeping track of various iterations of Commencal’s alloy Meta family of trail, all-mountain &amp; enduro bikes isn’t necessarily the easiest task. There’s been many <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=commencal+meta+am\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AM</a> enduro (since <em>all-mountain</em> predated <em>enduro</em> as a buzzword), <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=commencal+meta+tr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">TR</a> trail, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=commencal+meta+power\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Power</a> e-bike, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=commencal+meta+sx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SX</a> supercross, even <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/02/13/the-2020-commencal-meta-tr-sx-is-a-versatile-trail-bike-built-for-all-kinds-of-fun/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">TR SX</a> iterations –&nbsp; not to mention 26″, 27.5″ &amp; 29″ wheeled bikes in the Meta’s lifetime.</p><div id=\"attachment_273657\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273657\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, dark\" width=\"1350\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark.jpg 1350w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark-297x165.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark-800x444.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143325/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_dark-768x427.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1350px) 100vw, 1350px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273657\">c. Commencal</p></div><p>But there hasn’t yet been a Meta Mullet…. until now.</p><p>Commencal has already seen World Cup Downhill success with mullet versions of their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=commencal+supreme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Supreme DH</a> bike over the past few, so decided it was time to let enduro reap the same mixed 27/29 wheel benefits. But rather than slapping a small wheel or new swingarm into the back of the recently redesigned <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/06/22/commencals-2021-meta-am-29-goes-steep-and-slack-in-all-the-right-places/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Meta AM 29</a>, Commencal gave the bike a ground-up redesign with all-new geometry and tweaked suspension kinematics.</p><h3>What’s new</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, Signature edition detail\" width=\"1450\" height=\"850\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail.jpg 1450w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail-297x174.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail-800x469.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail-120x70.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143322/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_meta-sx-signature-detail-768x450.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1450px) 100vw, 1450px\"></a></p><p>The new mullet Meta SX looks almost identical to the new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/06/22/commencals-2021-meta-am-29-goes-steep-and-slack-in-all-the-right-places/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Meta AM 29</a> because they are effectively built with exactly the same technical parameters. What’s new is a subtle rebalancing of the new mixed wheelsize SX to maximize the trail-taming rollover &amp; grip of the 29″ front wheel and the more snappy acceleration and maneuverability of a 27.5″ rear wheel.</p><p>That’s essentially the exact same “marketing speak” of every other mullet bike you’ve read about for the past few years, so what did Commencal do differently?</p><h3>New Enduro geometry again</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, 29er front 27.5&quot; rear\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143319/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_29-front-275-rear-768x461.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>Just over a year ago, Commencal gave the 29er Meta AM a major geometry overhaul based on feedback from their EWS racers. That made the AM 29 frame much longer and slacker with longer wheelbases than its 27.5″ predecessor, plus steeper seattube angles and more standover. All for a faster &amp; more stable big-wheeled enduro race bike.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, geometry\" width=\"1500\" height=\"650\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry-297x129.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry-800x347.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry-120x52.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143315/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_new-geometry-768x333.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>But to get the same balanced ride out of a mixed wheel setup, Commencal shortened the Meta SX reach back 10mm, steepened the headtube angle back about half a degree on the smaller bikes, raised the bottom bracket 25mm, and actually lengthened the chainstays 9-14mm to better compliment the smaller rear wheel. they say the result is a more natural rider position in between the different sized wheels while reaping the benefits of each wheel size’s strengths.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, frame\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143312/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-angled-rear-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The mullet SX bike does also get a “more lively” suspension kinematics update, adapted from the new big-wheeled bike to suit this new geometry and a more agile style of riding. Commencal says, “<em>the result is a bike that is more agile and easier in the steeps, more efficient under braking and more dynamic when pushing hard</em>.”</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, frame\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143309/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_angled-frame-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The new 160mm travel, triple-butted 6066 t4/6 alloy Meta SX frame gets the same upgraded suspension design of the Meta AM 29 with increased rear end stiffness for the new double-row Enduro bearings. Claimed frame weight is 3.9kg. It also still gets 170mm 29″ forks up front.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, frame details\" width=\"1500\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details-297x158.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details-800x427.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details-120x64.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143306/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-details-768x410.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>The small flip chip is also still there at the lower shock mount on the linkage extension to give riders a bit of angle &amp; BB height adjustment to tailor to an individual’s riding style. The new bike also gets the latest internal cable routing &amp; external guide updates for a smoother running drivetrain.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, photoshoot\" width=\"1500\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot-297x158.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot-800x427.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot-120x64.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143303/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_signature-photoshoot-768x410.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>The bike features a ZS44/ZS56 headset for a tapered 1.5″ fork, a PressFit BB92 bottom bracket, ISCG05 tabs, Boost 148 spacing, 200mm post mount brake tabs, a 34.9mm seatpost with stealth dropper routing, and max 68mm (2.6″) tire clearance. The frame comes with integrated downtube, chainstay &amp; seatstay protectors, the 12mm rear axle, and pre-cut foam liners to quiet internal cable routing rattle.</p><h3>2022 Commencal Meta SX mullet&nbsp; – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, frame-only\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143300/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_frame-only-chrome-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>The new mullet Meta SX is being offered in seven different complete bike builds, and an individual frame option. The 2022 Commencal Meta SX frame sells for 1900€ in five different paint jobs without a shock. And from 400€ more you can use Commencal’s custom À La Carte configuration tool to add air or coil shocks from Fox, RockShox or Öhlins, too. Frame-only is the quickest way to get ahold of the new bike, with delivery as early as January 2022.</p><div id=\"attachment_273648\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273648\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, Origin complete\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1100\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin-297x163.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin-800x440.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin-120x66.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin-768x422.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143255/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Origin-1536x845.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273648\">2022 Commencal Meta SX Origin</p></div><div id=\"attachment_273647\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273647\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, Ride\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1100\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete-297x163.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete-800x440.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete-120x66.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete-768x422.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143251/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ride-complete-1536x845.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273647\">2022 Commencal Meta SX Ride</p></div><p>Complete builds start at just 3000€ for the Commencal Meta SX Origin with RockShox Domain R / Deluxe Select suspension &amp; SX Eagle; or 3300€ for the Commencal Meta SX Ride with RockShox Zeb / Deluxe Select+ &amp;&nbsp; SX Eagle,&nbsp;with those bikes available for pre-order now for February-April 2022 deliveries.</p><div id=\"attachment_273646\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273646\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta SX alloy mullet enduro bike, Ohlins\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1150\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete-297x171.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete-800x460.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete-120x69.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete-768x442.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143248/2022-Commencal-Meta-SX-mullet-enduro-bike_Meta-SX-Ohlins-complete-1536x883.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273646\">2022 Commencal Meta SX Öhlins</p></div><p>The price will likely at least double that for the Signature or Öhlins Editions of the new mullet Meta SX but deliveries are so far out later into 2022 that Commencal isn’t even announcing pricing yet.</p><h3>A Meta Power SX e-bike version of the new Meta Mullet, too!</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta Power SX mullet enduro e-bike eMTB\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143453/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_frameset-only-768x461.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>And don’t forget the new Meta Power SX either. The new eMTB mullet gets all the same performance upgrades, powered by a more-compact, lighter new Shimano EP8 motor and a massive 630Wh downtube battery.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Commencal Meta Power SX mullet enduro e-bike eMTB\" width=\"1300\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon.jpg 1300w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon-297x171.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon-800x462.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon-120x69.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/05143242/2022-Commencal-Meta-Power-SX-mullet-enduro-eMTB-e-bike_coming-soon-768x443.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px\"></a></p><p>You’ll have to wait though. No word yet of e-bike mullet Meta Power pricing, but deliveries are slated for the second &amp; third quarters of 2022…</p><p><a href=\"https://www.commencal-store.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Commencal-Store.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"60d815ec7e9039f49119359de91bc335ab64e35e3f0792cc794a5deef6b793b1","category":"Cycling"}